{"word":"γραπτέος","slug":"γραπτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γραπτέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:γράφω'><el>γράφω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>one must describe</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>γραπτέος, η, ον</el>, <i>to be described</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}